::Hot Rod::

He opened a comm to Najah.
"I dont think Zardus would like that. Feline is to important to the
Alliance. If you were to touch her, you would be scrap. And if you want
to fight with..."
He is cut off when he pulls to the left to avoid the energy shot.
"If you want to fight me, thats fine. You will die! Do you really think
you can kill the destroyer of Unicron?! Hot Rod Maximize!"
He transformes to bot mode.
"Now you face an Autobot!"
He fires two signature seeking rockets at Najah.
"Now you go to the pit!"
